00:18:03,033 --> 00:18:08,395
engine, if there's an existing art team or art director or just like a lone artist even,

365
00:18:08,395 --> 00:18:11,496
because it's good to let a new person know who they'd be working with.

366
00:18:12,897 --> 00:18:19,079
you know, if there is an absolutely non-negotiable budget, include that.

